  "body": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Lios Universal Village Mod Compatibility Datapack</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div>\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>Datapack enhances <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/lios-overhauled-villages\">Lio's Overhauled Villages</a> by providing universal compatibility with other popular mods. This data pack ensures smooth integration for a cohesive and immersive adventure with your favorite mods. Additions to more villager addon mods will be made in the future and will be updated here.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h2>Current Compatibilities</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ice-and-fire-dragons\">Ice and Fire</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pneumaticcraft-repressurized\">Pneumaticcraft</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dynamic-village\">Create Dynamic Village</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;-&nbsp; <strong>More to come!</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.12); border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03);\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/lioloader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; text-decoration: none;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/wrK85wgc/logo.png\" alt=\"LioLoader\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" style=\"display:block; border-radius: 12px;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.35;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: inherit;\">Need datapack-based configuration?</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: inherit; opacity: 0.9;\">\n        Check out <strong>LioLoader</strong> for global datapack / resource pack loading. Available for <strong>NeoForge</strong> and <strong>Fabric</strong> on <strong>Minecraft 1.21.x</strong>.\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: inherit; opacity: 0.85; margin-top: 4px;\">Open LioLoader on Modrinth →</div>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6n4z5RJ/1.png\" alt=\"1\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VTTTXFt/2.png\" alt=\"2\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/qFTZzbS/3.png\" alt=\"3\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/KKNyR68/4.png\" alt=\"4\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/34fdZTk/5.png\" alt=\"5\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/JcjKd6d/6.png\" alt=\"6\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<h2>Compatibility</h2>\n<p>This data pack works independently and will provide support for mods only if they're installed.</p>\n</div>\n<h2><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/b38h9pBFzC\"><br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/qDNhg49/636e0a6a49cf127bf92de1e2-icon-clyde-blurple-RGB.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"97\" /><br /></a></h2>\n<div>\n<p>Thank you for using Lios Universal Village Mod Compatibility Datapack! We hope you enjoy the enhanced Minecraft experience with <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/lios-overhauled-villages\">Lio's Overhauled Villages</a>!</p>\n</div>",
